column119: Helt Rent i Køge is looking for full-time cleaning assistants for cleaning in private homes as well as a few companies, working 30-37 hours per week. It is required that you have a category B driver’s license and can speak and understand Danish. We expect you to be: • Reliable and flexible • Independent and responsible • Approachable Non-negotiable requirements: • A criminal record must be provided. Flexible requirements: • It is not required to have prior cleaning experience, but it is essential that you are dedicated to delivering high-quality work. Attention to small details and effort in every task are a must. We do not compromise on cleanliness, so you must see yourself as part of this commitment. We operate across the entire island of Zealand. Working hours are from 7 AM to 3 PM, as well as every other Saturday. We offer: • Flexible working hours • Independence and freedom with responsibility • Thorough training • A dynamic and varied work environment If you meet all our expectations, we start with a salary of DKK 150 per hour. Would you like to join Denmark’s best cleaning team? Send your application and CV to Katja.rossi@hotmail.com or, if you have questions, call +45 28952705.
